                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240603-55-off287 t18240603-55-crimeloc290"></join>. On Saturday, the 24th of April, I went out about one o'clock, leaving a pair of snuffers in the shop - I returned<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182406030020"></xptr>about four or five o'clock, and saw the prisoners at the door. I missed the snuffers; I went to my brother, and said,</p>
               <p>"I believe these lads have robbed me." They ran across the fields.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18240603-55-person506">
                  JOHN 
                  THOMPSON
