                  </persName>
            . I am Mrs. Oldham's brother. I went out and pursued the lads; they had been walking, but ran away. I got within a few yards of them, and saw Palmer take the snuffers from his pocket, and throw them away; the other was some distance behind him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18240603-55-person507">
